{
  "file": "1514_Saavedra Lopez 等 - 2019 - Oligomerization of ethanol-derived propene and isobutene mixtures to transportation fuels catalyst.txt",
  "model": "deepseek-chat",
  "experiment_info": {
    "experiment_count": 3,
    "experiments": [
      {
        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "寡聚反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Oligomerization reaction",
        "description": "使用二异丁烯（DIB）作为模型原料，在1.38 MPa压力、WHSV为1.1 h⁻¹的条件下，在140°C、200°C和260°C三个温度下，评估了一系列固体酸催化剂（H-ZSM-5、H-Y、H-beta、USY沸石和Amberlyst-36、Purolite-CT275树脂）的催化性能。",
        "text_snippet": "Two representative model olefin feeds: 1) diisobutene and 2) isobutene/propene (4/1 mol) mixture were used... DIB was used as a model feed for the oligomerization reaction over the series of solid acid catalysts presented in Table 1... Performance evaluations for the oligomerization catalysts were performed in a single fixed-bed reactor... (1.38 MPa, WHSV = 1.1 h−1).",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Oligomer-Isomer reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "寡聚反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Oligomerization reaction",
        "description": "使用异丁烯/丙烯（4:1 摩尔比）混合物作为模型原料，在1.38 MPa压力、WHSV为1.1 h⁻¹的条件下，在不同温度下（H-beta沸石：140°C, 200°C, 260°C；CT275树脂：100°C, 120°C；Amberlyst-36树脂：140°C）评估了H-beta沸石和聚合物树脂（CT275, Amberlyst-36）的催化性能。",
        "text_snippet": "Two representative model olefin feeds: 1) diisobutene and 2) isobutene/propene (4/1 mol) mixture were used... an isobutene/propene mixture (4:1 molar ratio) was used as a model feedstock... Oligomerization results are shown in Table 3 and Fig. 4 using, H-beta, the most promising zeolite determined from above, and compared to the polymeric resins CT275 and Amberlyst-36.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Oligomer-Isomer reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 3,
        "reaction_type": "寡聚反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Oligomerization reaction",
        "description": "集成两步法工艺实验：第一步，在450°C、1.38 MPa压力下，使用Zn₁Zr₂.₅O₂催化剂将50 wt%乙醇/水混合物转化为富含异丁烯和丙烯的烯烃混合物。第二步，在140°C、WHSV为1.1 h⁻¹的条件下，使用Amberlyst-36催化剂将第一步产生的烯烃（经氧合物分离后）进行寡聚，运行时间达350小时。",
        "text_snippet": "Processing of aqueous ethanol to liquid hydrocarbon product was demonstrated in two sequential catalytic steps: 1)conversion of ethanol to an isobutene/propene-rich gas mixture over ZnZr O catalyst, followed by 2)oligomerization over solid acid resin(Amberlyst-36)... Catalytic activity tests for the conversion of aqueous ethanol to primarily gasoline-range hydrocarbons were conducted in a two-step process using two reactors in series... This reactor was operated at ... WHSV = 1.1 h−1... operated for 350 hours TOS.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Oligomer-Isomer reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
